<HEADLINE> Earlier Alaska Air Problems Reported  </HEADLINE>
   By LINDA DEUTSCH AP Special Correspondent
<TEXT>
<P>
	   PORT HUENEME, Calif. (AP) -- Investigators said Wednesday they are looking
